Test "Mint WBTC then redeem with reserves and interest"
    NewComptroller
    ListedGToken WBTC gWBTC initialExchangeRate:0.1 tokenType:WBTC
    Prep Geoff 50e8 WBTC gWBTC
    Mint Geoff 50e8 gWBTC
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gWBTC TokenBalance Geoff) 500e8
    Assert Equal (GToken gWBTC UnderlyingBalance Geoff) 50e8
    Assert Equal (GToken gWBTC ExchangeRate) 0.1
    -- Get some brah to borrow then repay
    BorrowAndRepayWithInterest WBTC gWBTC 10e8 5e8 interestRate:0.000001 blocks:500000 reserveRate:0.2
    -- We've accrued .001% interest for 500000 blocks, or 50% of the principal,
    --   thus, we should have accrued 5e8 of interest for the protocol
    --   The reserves should get 20% of this, or 1e8, and the rest
    --   is due pro-rata to all suppliers. We just have one, so
    --   let's check that account is given correct new balance.
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gWBTC TokenBalance Geoff) 500e8
    Assert Equal (GToken gWBTC Reserves) 1e8
    Assert Equal (GToken gWBTC UnderlyingBalance Geoff) 54e8
    -- 55e8 + 0e8 - 1e8 / 500
    Assert Equal (GToken gWBTC ExchangeRate) 0.108
    -- Now redeem all with interest
    Redeem Geoff 500e8 gWBTC
    Assert Equal (Erc20 WBTC TokenBalance Geoff) 54e8
    Assert Equal (Erc20 WBTC TokenBalance gWBTC) 1e8
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gWBTC TokenBalance Geoff) 0e8
    Assert Equal (GToken gWBTC Reserves) 1e8
    Assert Equal (GToken gWBTC UnderlyingBalance Geoff) 0e8
    Assert Equal (GToken gWBTC ExchangeRate) 0.1

Test "Two users Mint WBTC, one redeems"
    NewComptroller
    ListedGToken WBTC gWBTC initialExchangeRate:0.1 tokenType:WBTC
    Prep Geoff Some WBTC gWBTC
    Prep Torrey Some WBTC gWBTC
    Mint Geoff 2e8 gWBTC
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gWBTC TokenBalance Geoff) 20e8
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gWBTC TotalSupply) 20e8
    Mint Torrey 2e8 gWBTC
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gWBTC TokenBalance Geoff) 20e8
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gWBTC TokenBalance Torrey) 20e8
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gWBTC TotalSupply) 40e8
    Redeem Torrey 10e8 gWBTC
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gWBTC TokenBalance Geoff) 20e8
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gWBTC TokenBalance Torrey) 10e8
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gWBTC TotalSupply) 30e8

